data.title: Phillip Edmunds Spalding Jr. (1918-1999) – Find a...
data.meta_description: Kamaaina businessman Philip Edmunds Spalding Jr. died in Mijas, Spain, on Saturday. He was 80. Spalding served as president of Molokai Ranch from 1973 to 1988. During his 15 years as chief executive officer, he initiated the diversification program that led to the development of the island's first major resort,...
